Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------op--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}戻らない時間に溺れぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今を抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その微笑みを行ったり来たり　そばにいたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この手を伸ばす　先には何が待ってるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}終わらない物語の向こう　飛び立て
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の気持ちでたどり着く場所へと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の翼を広げて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}廻りゆくメッセージ　幸せは胸にあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あと少しの勇気　涙も必要なの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}強くなれるチャンスかもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温もりのリフレイン　この大切をずっと守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心を重ねてく　絆を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も一人じゃないんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ空の下　確かな想いを伝えたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:06.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这份真情实感　好想将它传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:18.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不沉溺于一去不返的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:21.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧拥抱今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:28.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷于那微笑之中　好想相伴在你的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:36.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出手　前方应该有什么正等待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:42.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着那未完结的故事　飞奔而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀着一颗真诚的心向着那千难万险之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}张开心灵的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:58.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}循环传递着一个讯息　幸福就存于这胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:02.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}接下来的少许勇气　尽管须以眼泪相佐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:06.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但这或许正是变强的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:12.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}温暖的迭句　想要永远将这份珍重守护
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:16.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彼此心绪交织　感受着这其中的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:20.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以说没有人是孤身只影的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:29.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同一片蓝天下　好想将这份真情实感传递
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------ed--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の奥集めた　今日の光を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飛び込んだ未知の先　何が待ってるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}未来への共鳴　想い出に重ねれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気になる　強さになる　一人じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（聴かせて）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日もきっと会えるね　本当の笑顔で行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢見る夜明けを　一緒に迎えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無限の時間よりも　瞬間を駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}その夢の声いつか聴かせてね　信じてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:19.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怀揣着内心深处收集好了的今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:28.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}跃入未知的前方　那里有什么正等待着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:37.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若是与未来共鸣　不断忆起今天的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:46.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就会生出勇气　就能变得坚强　也就不再是独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:49.05,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}（让你倾听）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天也一定会与你相遇　我会带着真诚的笑容前去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.86,0:23:06.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好想和你一起迎接梦想中的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.72,0:23:15.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}与其坐拥这无限的时刻　倒不如追赶那绚烂的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:26.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}相信我　总有一天会让你倾听那梦中的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  千秋啊  欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  熊田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便坐吧  正好找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能先借下体温计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有些发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天嘛  天气又暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还是那么随便的下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  我有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于千秋你们班主任田中老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我看看  我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36度9  是不是该休息下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度不高就算了  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看错了  是37度1啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确点儿是37度1分9厘  休息5分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就稍微休息会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  田中老师怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.86,0:02:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  田中老师挺优秀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健老师熊田刚好凑巧  目前正好没男朋友哦  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能这么告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够腹黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要柠檬汽水糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  总觉得很可怕  免了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  我觉得有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  貌似没发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  拿着  以防万一给你点儿药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊  舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  下午的课要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是柠檬汽水糖吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不过是精神疲劳罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会麻烦你负责救护了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:41.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}第12碗  一口也吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近回来得很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在干什么可疑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当上运动会的负责人  有不少事要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还能有别的什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责什么呢  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责救护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  为什么这个时候开运动会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的小学还真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会真令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点儿回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少动嘴多动手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是回去晚点儿嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用扔下我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.03,0:05:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁害的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你讨厌他？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,态度太冷淡了吧  明明是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家也不一起走…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为偶然住在隔壁  就必须一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夏奈叫来的  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在为运动会做特训
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别歇着了  特训还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？还来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了  不经过努力又何来胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在运动会这华丽的舞台上取得好成绩  就只有特训了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.55,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  教练
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你要不要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要陪你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐她们好像玩得很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是犯傻罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:06:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说什么就快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学  是个有趣的运动会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛突然说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个拐弯抹角的家伙  搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这些也能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨能停就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气预报说会放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天听说  隔壁那家又要搬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁  有些漫画我还没看过  现在去借
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁他们打包之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…明天再去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜  实在是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个多好的家伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得亲近起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  还有这么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么惯着她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木负责折纸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马负责把纸展开成花的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责绑线去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起来很快就干完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少动嘴多动手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  虽然现在说晚了点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都姓「南」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我冬马就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  叫我千秋就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起  冬马同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫法也很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备  跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉～运动会加上隔壁邻居搬家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们家事还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是春天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得跟季节无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有个家伙什么季节都很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你也参加什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有家属也能参加的比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢  我得问问千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么悠闲自在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  南春香要参加运动会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想千秋一定很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得去参加社团活动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～今天好丰盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为明天是运动会了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去给你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话  在运动会上加油可是家人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起加油  运动会才热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人聚在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望明天能放晴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始举行运动会开幕式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午餐就交给我了  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈…为什么你会？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人叫你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好嘛  和我们一起加油吧  藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面是第五个比赛项目  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年级学生的百米赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋她们要参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:14:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  内田  吉野  让大家看看特训的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们自己搞定  一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加借物跑的五年级学生  请马上集合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么带着夏奈跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个  因为没别的合适人选了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  为什么拉着藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在够爆笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈是父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:37.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是父亲？明明只有初二啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是各班代表参加的化装游行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班的代表是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和穿女装的阿真好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里  上午的比赛项目全部结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去教室里吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人没有来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么也没干  别第一个就下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你加油也是很耗能量的啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木也别客气  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.36,0:16:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次跟这么多人一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点儿吃就没了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  下午有项目需要家属参加  你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？有那样的项目吗  我怎么没听说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没打算让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是让春香参加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了  我也想参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是参加过了吗  借物跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想参加别的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我再陪你参加一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何如何  没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和南同学…是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我为今天而准备的…最强的手制意大利面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水温也必须达到最佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一份那不勒斯风味的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的比赛马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.99,0:18:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请同学们各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是第二十七个比赛项目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年级学生与爸爸或妈妈的两人三脚赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位  预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那么紧张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会到这里就正式闭幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有没有意式黑胡椒面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意式香辣面还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会再收拾不也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了  快点儿干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…为什么冬木不待到最后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬木呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他今天转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没听说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他硬是要参加上午的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都来了就待到最后嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么就直说啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷  春天还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大早上起来就那么多废话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷就是冷  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说废话也不会暖和起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回来做点热乎的东西当点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午没课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有春香没课太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定今天上完上午的课就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！别无视我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  交换留学生已经决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我打算让南同学去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都没跟我们说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么内情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送别会要办得盛大一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  来得正好  快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:21:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗…骗人的吧  我都没听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家常的醋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实在洗衣服时也有大用处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微倒入一点儿来代替柔顺剂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:36.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服就会变得很柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不会留下醋味  可以放心使用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对防止面料退色也很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因衣服质地不同也会有不适用的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请事先调查好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:54.73,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\an8\fad(250,0)}第十三碗  「大家在一起、承蒙款待」
